deploy(address,address,address,uint24,in.details: Deploys a pool with the given parameters by transiently setting the parameters storage slot and then clearing it after deploying the pool.

params.factory: The contract address of the PancakeSwap V3 factory
params.fee: The fee collected upon every swap in the pool, denominated in hundredths of a bip
params.token0: The first token of the pool by address sort order
params.token1: The second token of the pool by address sort order

parameters().notice: Get the parameters to be used in constructing the pool, set transiently during pool creation.

documentation.text: @notice Emitted when factory address is set
